80
00:07:43,130 --> 00:07:44,330
Gwen Stacy.

81
00:07:44,710 --> 00:07:46,340
Được rồi.

82
00:07:47,590 --> 00:07:49,260
Chào bác!

83
00:07:49,420 --> 00:07:50,340
